00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.220
" And this is exactly what I tried to tell you all in April whenever I came out in March.

00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:36.091
It was probably February whenever the Lord told me, "The month of April will be during the eclipse.

00:00:36.091 --> 00:00:59.050
" I said nothing will happen during the eclipse, but after the eclipse happens, because of Passover, during that time frame, there will be an acceleration of war, an acceleration with the weather, an acceleration with financial things, and an acceleration of signs in the heavens.

00:01:02.061 --> 00:01:13.154
