00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:09.520
Back whenever I started interceding for this and telling you all about this, nothing was in the news about Iran really wanting to do anything.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:17.680
Now they're saying they're at war, and then Iran is saying, "Hey, we're not going to do anything.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.191
This was our only little thing.

00:02:21.191 --> 00:02:21.858
" They're liars.

00:02:21.858 --> 00:02:23.936
They're planning something.

00:02:36.059 --> 00:02:36.329
