00:11:56.023 --> 00:12:05.703
As an American, I felt we should be watchful about churches, stadiums, and our surroundings, even when in church.

00:12:05.703 --> 00:12:17.984
Pray and obey, plead the blood over your congregation, and drive around your church to plead the blood.

