00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Whatever you call us to do, we do it with great victory and with the anointing of the Holy Spirit.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
I thank you, Father, that you say if we draw nigh unto you, you come nigh unto us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I thank you, Lord, that we have a revelation of who we are in Christ in these last days.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
And we give you all the glory, honor, and praise for it in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Amen.

